		function refreshApsBids(status = {}, slot = false) {
			var slotsToRefresh;
			if(slot) {
				slotsToRefresh = slots.find(function(val) {
					return val.slotName == slot;
				});
				slotsToRefresh = [slotsToRefresh];
				console.log('[Amazon] Found to refresh', slotsToRefresh);
			} else {
				slotsToRefresh = slots;
			}
			status.apsDone = false;
			// request the bids for the four googletag slots
			if(slotsToRefresh) {
				apstag.fetchBids({
					slots: slotsToRefresh
				}, function(bids) {
					// set apstag bids
					googletag.cmd.push(function() {
						console.log('[Amazon] Finished');
						apstag.setDisplayBids();
						/* Disabled for coordination with Prebid */
						/* googletag.pubads().refresh(); */
						status.apsDone = true;
					});
				});
			} else {
				console.log("[Amazon] Can't find slot to refresh: ", slot);
				status.apsDone = true;
			}
		}
		refreshApsBids(initialLoadStatus);

		if(dc_ad_home) {

		} else {
			pbLabels.push('article');
		}
	
		function refreshPbjsBids(status = {}, slotName = false) {
			pbjs.que.push(function() {
				status.pbjsDone = false;
				pbjs.setConfig({
					priceGranularity: "high",
					sizeConfig: [
						{
							mediaQuery: '(min-width: ' + String(dcRespMaxW + 1) + 'px)',
							sizesSupported: [].concat(dailycaller_top_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_right1_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_sticky_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_inline_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_inline1_desktop_sizes),
							labels: ["desktop"]
						}, {
							mediaQuery: '(min-width: ' + String(dcRespMinW) + 'px) and (max-width: ' +String(dcRespMaxW) + 'px)',
							sizesSupported: [].concat(dailycaller_top_tablet_sizes, dailycaller_inline_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_inline1_desktop_sizes, dailycaller_sticky_tablet_sizes),
							labels: ["tablet"]
						}, {
							mediaQuery: '(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: ' +String(dcRespMinW - 1) + 'px)',
							sizesSupported: [].concat(dailycaller_top_mobile_sizes, dailycaller_inline_mobile_sizes, dailycaller_sticky_mobile_sizes),
							labels: ["mobile"]
						}
					],
					userSync: {
						userIds: [{
							name: "identityLink",
							params: {
								pid: "1263"
							},
							storage: {
								type: "cookie",
								name: "idl_env",
								expires: 7
							}
						}],
					}
				});
				pbjs.enableAnalytics({
					provider: 'ga',
					options: {
					}
				});
				pbjs.removeAdUnit();
				if(!slotName) {
					pbjs.addAdUnits(adUnits);
				} else {
					var filtered = [adUnits.find(function(el) {
						return el.code == slotName;
					})];
					pbjs.addAdUnits(filtered);
				}
				pbjs.requestBids({
					bidsBackHandler: function(bids, timedOut) {
						console.log('[Prebid] Finished');
						pbjs.setTargetingForGPTAsync();
						status.pbjsDone = true;
						/* Disabled for coordination with Amazon */
						/* googletag.pubads().refresh(); */
					},
					timeout: PREBID_TIMEOUT,
					labels: pbLabels
				});
			});
		}
		refreshPbjsBids(initialLoadStatus);
	
		function loadBids(status = {}) {
			/* This is the final coordination between Amazon and Prebid */
			var dcRefreshIntervalStart = Date.now();
			function dcRefreshIntervalCheck() {
				var runTime = Date.now() - dcRefreshIntervalStart;
				if(FAILSAFE_TIMEOUT + 25 < runTime || (status.apsDone && status.pbjsDone)) {
					console.log('[Google] Submitting');
					clearInterval(dcRefreshInterval);
					googletag.pubads().refresh();
				}
			}
			var dcRefreshInterval = setInterval(dcRefreshIntervalCheck, 50);
		};
		loadBids(initialLoadStatus);
	
		/* Refresh everything */
	googletag.cmd.push(function() {
		var REFRESH_TIMEOUT = 30;
		googletag.pubads().addEventListener('impressionViewable', function(e) {
			if(dc_disable_refresh) {
				return;
			}
			var slot = e.slot;
			var slotName = slot.getAdUnitPath();
			console.log('[Ads] Impression Viewable for ', slotName);
			setTimeout(function() {
				console.log('[Ads] Refreshing ', slotName);
				var status = {};
				if (slot.getTargeting('refresh').indexOf('true') > -1) {
					refreshApsBids(status, slotName);
					refreshPbjsBids(status, slotName);
					var intervalStart = Date.now();
					var interval;
					function intervalCheck() {
						var runTime = Date.now() - intervalStart;
						if(FAILSAFE_TIMEOUT + 25 < runTime || (status.apsDone && status.pbjsDone)) {
							console.log('[Google] Submitting refresh');
							clearInterval(interval);
							googletag.pubads().refresh([slot]);
						}
					}
					interval = setInterval(intervalCheck, 50);
				}
			}, REFRESH_TIMEOUT * 1000);
		});
	});
  </script>

   document.cookie = "__adblocker=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 GMT; path=/";
	var setNptTechAdblockerCookie = function(adblocker) {
	var d = new Date();
	d.setTime(d.getTime() + 60 * 60 * 24 * 2 * 1000);
	document.cookie = "__adblocker=" + (adblocker ? "true" : "false") + "; expires=" + d.toUTCString() + "; path=/";
	};
	var script = document.createElement("script");
	script.setAttribute("async", true);
	script.setAttribute("src", "//www.npttech.com/advertising.js");
	script.setAttribute("onerror", "setNptTechAdblockerCookie(true);");
	document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0].appendChild(script);
  </script>

  <script>
   var wWidth = (function windowWidth() {
	    var docElemProp = window.document.documentElement.clientWidth,
	        body = window.document.body;
	    return window.document.compatMode === "CSS1Compat" && docElemProp || body && body.clientWidth || docElemProp;
	})();
	
	googletag.cmd.push( function() {
		googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRenderEnded', function(event) {
			console.log("DC AD: slotRenderEnded for " + event.slot.getAdUnitPath());
			console.log(event);
			if(event.isEmpty) {
				console.log("DC AD: Empty slot: " + event.slot.getAdUnitPath());
				if(event.slot.getAdUnitPath() == '/10519169/dailycaller_sticky') {
					document.getElementsByClassName("dc-sticky").display = "none";
				}
				if(event.slot.getAdUnitPath() == '/10519169/dailycaller_top'){
					document.getElementById("dailycaller_top").style.display = "block";
				}
				return;
			}
			if(event.size.width > 0) {
				document.querySelectorAll('div.ad div').style.width = '';
			}
			if(event.size.height > 0) {
				document.querySelectorAll('div.ad div').style.height = '';
			}
			switch(event.slot.getAdUnitPath()) {
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_top':
					document.querySelectorAll("div[class='adcontainer']").forEach(box => { box.style.minHeight = "250px" })
					document.getElementById("dailycaller_top").style.backgroundColor = "transparent";
					document.querySelectorAll('#dailycaller_top [id^="google_ads_iframe_"]').forEach(item =>{item.style.position = "static"});
						if(document.querySelectorAll('#dailycaller_top [id^="google_ads_iframe_"]')[1].height === 90){
						document.querySelector('#dailycaller_top [id^="google_ads_iframe_/10519169/dailycaller_top_0__container__"]').style.paddingTop = "80px"
					}
					break;	
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_inline2':
					document.querySelector('#dailycaller_inline2, #\\/10519169\\/dailycaller_inline2').style.display = "block"
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_inline3':
					document.querySelector('#dailycaller_inline3, #\\/10519169\\/dailycaller_inline3').style.display = "block"
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_right1':
					if(wWidth >= dcRespMaxW) {
						var ifIsArticle = document.querySelector("article[class='max-w-lg mx-auto mb-6 mb-12 px-4 lg:pt-2']");
						if(!ifIsArticle){
							document.getElementById("dailycaller_right1").style.minHeight = "1010px";
							document.getElementById("dailycaller_right1").style.marginBottom = "40px";
						}
					}
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_left1':
					document.querySelector('#dailycaller_left1 div').style.position = "static";
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_left2':
					document.getElementById("dailycaller_left2").style.marginBottom = "40px";
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_home3':
					document.querySelector('#dailycaller_home3 div').style.position = "static"
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_home4':
					document.querySelector('#dailycaller_home4 div').style.position = "static"
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_interstitial':
					document.getElementById("dailycaller_interstitial").width = event.size[0];
					document.getElementById("dailycaller_interstitial").height = event.size[1];
					var dc_interstitial = document.getElementsByClassName("dc-interstitial");
					dc_interstitial[0].classList.remove("hidden");
					var closeButton = document.getElementById("dc-interstitial-close-button")
					var ad = document.getElementById("dailycaller_interstitial");
					ad.appendChild(closeButton);
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_sticky':
					console.log("DC Sticky: Opening!");
					var closeButton = document.querySelector(".dc-sticky [title='Close window']");
					closeButton.addEventListener('click', function(){
						document.querySelector(".dc-sticky").style.display = "none";
					});
					break;
				case '/10519169/dailycaller_skin':
					console.log('DC AD: SKIN disabling refresh');
					dc_disable_refresh = true;
					//console.log('DC AD: SKIN Opening!');
					var skinIframe = document.getElementById("google_ads_iframe_/10519169/dailycaller_skin_0")
					var skinIframeContDoc = skinIframe.contentDocument;
					var imgadpath = skinIframeContDoc.getElementsByClassName("img_ad");
					var imgad = imgadpath[0]["src"];
					var imghrefpath = skinIframeContDoc.getElementsByTagName("a");
					var imghref = imghrefpath[0].href;
	
					document.getElementsByTagName("body")[0].style.backgroundImage = 'url(' + imgad + ')';
					document.getElementsByTagName("body")[0].style.cursor = 'pointer';
	
					document.addEventListener("click", function(event){
						if (event && event.target == document.body) {
							window.open(imghref);
							console.log(`DC AD: SKIN: imghref is ${imghref}`);
							console.log(`DC AD: SKIN: imgad is ${imgad}`);
						}
						if (event.target.tagName == "MAIN"){
							window.open(imghref);
							console.log(`DC AD: SKIN: imghref is ${imghref}`);
							console.log(`DC AD: SKIN: imgad is ${imgad}`);
						}
					})				
	
					//console.log('DC AD: SKIN ' + imgad);
					//console.log('DC AD: SKIN ' + imghref);
					break;
	
			}		
		});
	});

   document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',function() {
		var played = {};
		var audioElement = document.getElementsByTagName('audio');
		audioElement.onplaying =  function(evt) {
			var src = this.window.firstChild;
			src = src.getAttribute('src');

				played[src] = true;
				(typeof ga == 'function') && ga('send', {
					hitType: 'event',
					eventCategory: 'Audio',
					eventAction: 'Play',

				});

		};

  <script>
   var dc_piano_emailAddr = "";
	
		function dc_piano_is_logged_in(data = false) {
			console.log('[Piano] dc_piano_is_logged_in begins');
			tp.user.refreshAccessToken(true);
			if(data) {
				dc_piano_emailAddr = data.user.email;
				console.log("[Piano]: Email address is ", dc_piano_emailAddr);
				//console.log('[Piano] User ', data.user, ' logged in with token', data.token);
				<!-- TAG: CivicScience IdSync -->
				var img = document.createElement('img');
				img.setAttribute("src", 'https://www.civicscience.com/idsync?uid=dailycaller:' + data.user.uid);
				img.setAttribute("width", "0");
				img.setAttribute("height", "0");
				document.body.appendChild(img);
			} else {
				//console.log('[Piano] User is logged in');
			}
			//console.log("[PIANO] the user id is ", data.user.uid);
			var pianoonoff = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-on-off')[0];
			pianoonoff.style.display = 'none';
			var pianologgedin = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-loggedin')[0];
			pianologgedin.style.display = 'block';
			var patsloginspon = document.querySelector('#patriots-log-in span');
			patsloginspon.innerHTML = "Log Out";
			
			tp.push(['addHandler', 'loginSuccess', function(){
				var d = data;
				var userid = d.user.uid;
				tp.api.callApi('/access/list', {}, function(dat){
					if(typeof dat.data != "undefined"){
						for(var i in dat.data){
							if(dat.data[i].granted){
								console.log("[PIANO]: user is paid subscriber");
								fbq('track', 'LogIntoAccount', {is_subscriber:true, subscription_id:userid});
							}
						}
					}
					if(dat.data.length === 0){
						console.log("[PIANO]: user is not paid subscriber");
						fbq('track', 'LogIntoAccount', {is_subscriber:false, subscription_id:userid});
					}
				});
			}]);
	
			tp.push(["addHandler", "checkoutCustomEvent", function(event){
				if(event.eventName === "FacebookPixelSignUp"){
				console.log("[PIANO] Sign Up Clicked");
				fbq('track', 'CompleteRegistration');
				}
			}]);
	
			tp.push(["addHandler", "loginSuccess", function(data){
				if(data.registration){
					console.log("[PIANO] signup upon registration complete!");
					fbq('track', 'CompleteRegistration');
				}
			}]);
	
	
			handleLiveRamp();
		}
		function dc_piano_is_logged_out() {
			console.log('[Piano] dc_piano_is_logged_out begins');
			document.cookie = '__tac=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;domain=.dailycaller.com;path=/;';
			var pianoonoff = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-on-off')[0];
			pianoonoff.style.display = 'block';
			var pianologgedin = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-loggedin')[0];
			pianologgedin.style.display = 'none';
			var patsloginspon = document.querySelector('#patriots-log-in span');
			patsloginspon.innerHTML = "Log In";
			ga('set', 'dimension9', 'false');
			handleLiveRamp();
		}
	
		function handleLiveRamp(){
			var atsScript = document.createElement('script');
			var atsObj = {
				"placementID": 1263,
				"storageType": "localStorage",
				"detectionType": "detect",
				"logging": "error"
			}
			
			if(dc_piano_emailAddr !== ""){
				atsObj["email"] = dc_piano_emailAddr;
				
			}
			console.log("[LIVERAMP]: atsObj is ", atsObj);
			
			
			atsScript.onload = function() {
			  window.ats.start(atsObj);
			  console.log("[LIVERAMP]: LiveRamp started! Email address is: ", dc_piano_emailAddr);
			};
			atsScript.src = 'https://ats.rlcdn.com/ats.js';
			document.body.appendChild(atsScript);
		}
	
		function dc_piano_do_login() {
			//console.log('[Piano] dc_piano_do_login begins');
			tp.pianoId.show({
				screen: 'login',
			});
			console.log("[dc_piano_do_login()]: logging in");
		}
		function dc_piano_do_logout() {
			//console.log('[Piano] dc_piano_do_logout begins');
			tp.pianoId.logout();
			console.log("[dc_piano_do_logout()]:now logged out!");
		}
	
		tp = window["tp"] || [];
		tp.push(["setUsePianoIdUserProvider", true ]);
	
		tp.push(["addHandler", "checkoutCustomEvent", function(event){ 
			switch(event.eventName) {
				case "offer-subscribe-0":
					fbq('track', 'AddToCart');
					console.log("[FACEBOOK PIXEL] monthly clicked")
					break;
				case "offer-subscribe-1":
					fbq('track', 'AddToCart');
					console.log("[FACEBOOK PIXEL] annual clicked");
					break;
			} 
		}]);
		
		tp.push(["addHandler", "experienceExecute", function(e){
			var experiences = e.result.experiences;
			window.dcExperienceExecuteExperiencesFound = experiences;
			if((experiences.filter(function(x){return ( x.id === "EX3I5KWTU1J1" )}).length > 0) && !dc_premiumcontent){
				console.log("[PIANO] paywall seen!");
				fbq('track', 'ViewPaywall', {surface:'IA'});
			}
		}]);
	
		tp.push(["addHandler","checkoutComplete",function(conversion){
			fbq('track', 'Purchase', {value:conversion.chargeAmount, currency: conversion.chargeCurrency});
			fbq('track', 'Subscribe', {currency: conversion.chargeCurrency,value:conversion.chargeAmount, subscription_id:conversion.uid});
			console.log("track Purchase should've been fired");
			gtag('event', 'conversion', {'send_to': 'AW-1022386933/uKyDCJWZwe8BEPXFwecD', 'value': conversion.chargeAmount,'currency': conversion.chargeCurrency});
			console.log("[FACEBOOK PIXEL] purchase made")
			setTimeout(function(){window.location.href = "/thank-you/"},5000);
		}]);
	
		tp.push(["init", function() {
			//console.log("[Piano] init begins");
			tp.enableGACrossDomainLinking();
	
			window.resetPianoCookie = false;
	
			tp.pianoId.init({
				displayMode: 'modal',
				width: 320,
				height: 460,
				containerSelector: '#piano-form',
				loggedIn: dc_piano_is_logged_in,
				loggedOut: dc_piano_is_logged_out
			});
			
			var dcpiano = document.getElementsByClassName("dc-piano")[0];
			dcpiano.style.top = "100%";
			//console.log("[Piano] window.resetPianoCookie: " + window.resetPianoCookie);
			console.log("[Piano] isUserValid: " + JSON.stringify(tp.pianoId.isUserValid()));
			if(window.resetPianoCookie || !tp.pianoId.isUserValid()) {
				dc_piano_do_logout();
			}
		}]);
		document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
			//console.log("[Piano] document.ready begins");
			var pianologin = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-login')[0];
			pianologin.addEventListener('click',function(){
				dc_piano_do_login();
			})
			var pianoonandoff = document.getElementsByClassName('piano-on-off')[0];
			pianoonandoff.addEventListener('click',function(){
				tp.offer.show({
					displayMode: "modal"
				});			
			})
		});
	
		tp.push(["addHandler", "checkoutSelectTerm", function(termDetails, iframeId){
			console.log("[PIANO]: term details are ", termDetails);
			var offerId = termDetails.offerId;
			fbq('track', 'InitiateCheckout', {offer_code:offerId});
		}]);
  </script>
  <script>
   var cX = cX || {}; cX.callQueue = cX.callQueue || [];
		cX.callQueue.push(["invoke", function invoke(){
			cX.getUserSegmentIds({persistedQueryId: "a96dde9271c0619885346f258b7db0df6ae39b6c", callback: function callback(segmentIds){
				if(document.readyState === "complete"){
					if(typeof fbq !== "undefined"){
						setTimeout(function(){
							fbq("trackCustom", "CxSegments", {segmentIds: segmentIds})},5)
					}
				}
				else{
					var earlyOnReadyStateChange = document.onreadystatechange;
					document.onreadystatechange = function onReadyStateChange(){
						if(earlyOnReadyStateChange){
							earlyOnReadyStateChange();
						}
						if(document.readyState === "complete"){
							if(typeof fbq !== "undefined"){
								setTimeout(function(){
									fbq("trackCustom", "CxSegments", {segmentIds: segmentIds})},5)
							}
						}
					};
				}
			}});
		}]);
  </script>
  <script>
   function handleMixi(){
	
			  var mixiAds;
	
			  window.addEventListener("load", function(event){
			    mixiAds = document.querySelector("#unit_93914");
			    createObserver();
			  },false);
	
			  function createObserver(){
			    var observer;
	
			    var options = {
			      root: null,
			      rootMargin: "0px",
			      threshold: 0.2
			    };
	
			    observer = new IntersectionObserver(handleIntersect, options);
			    observer.observe(mixiAds);
	
			  }
	
	
			  function handleIntersect(entries,observer){
			    
			    for (var i = 0; i < entries.length; i++){
			      if(entries[i].isIntersecting){
			        var sc = document.createElement('script'); sc.type = 'text/javascript'; sc.async = true;
			        sc.src = '//mixi.media/data/js/93914.js'; sc.charset = 'utf-8';
			        var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(sc, s);
			        observer.unobserve(mixiAds);
			        }
			      }   
			    }
	
			}
			handleMixi();
  </script>
 </body>
</html>
